description.en: GNG is positioned as a universal token in the global gold industry. It uses a new generation of blockchain technology to ensure the authenticity and transparency of GNG. Its main purpose is to play the incentive role of the industry general token, including encouraging consumers to buy, enhancing the sales of merchants, and improving the retention rate and loyalty of consumers. GNG has been dedicated to serving merchants and consumers in the global gold industry.
